  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述任务的生命周期。初始状态应该是Active，然后Active内部要有Running和Paused两种子状态，可以互相切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Active",
        "Running",
        "Paused"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以Active是一个复合状态，里面包含Running和Paused。那Running和Paused之间怎么切换？是用pause和resume这两个事件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Running",
        "Paused",
        "pause",
        "resume"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Running可以pause到Paused，Paused可以resume回到Running。另外整个Active状态应该能直接stop结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Paused",
        "pause",
        "resume",
        "Active",
        "stop",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画个初稿。用stateDiagram-v2，把Active做成一个state块，里面放Running和Paused的双向转换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "Active",
        "Running",
        "Paused"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Active内部还需要一个初始状态指向Running，不然不知道默认进哪个子状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "[*]",
        "Running"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，Active里面的[*]指向Running。现在结构是：从全局起点到Active，Active内部默认到Running，然后pause/resume循环，最后Active可以stop到终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Active",
        "Running",
        "Paused",
        "pause",
        "resume",
        "stop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来没问题。确认一下：stop是从Active直接到结束状态，不是从Running或Paused出去的吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "stop",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，stop是Active -- [*]，从复合状态直接退出。这样整个状态图就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "stop",
        "[*]"
      ],
